snippet.title: Harpy Gaiden trailer
snippet.description:
The official trailer for Harpy Gaiden!

Harpy Gaiden is a platformer where you play as a harpy, take to the skies and utilize your bow in this cute little side-story to the Day in the Life of a Harpy series.

Check out more Xysspon games at https://xysspon.com/

This video does not use footage from the final build of this game.
